manı: Zabbix Yapısının Kurulması

Müşterilerde ortalama threshold değerlerini hesaplamak için sorgu:

```sql
SELECT
	RunType,
	MIN(TotalDuration) MinDuration,
	AVG(TotalDuration) AvgDuration,
	MAX(TotalDuration) MaxDuration,
	MIN(ProductCount) MinProductCount,
	AVG(ProductCount) AvgProductCount,
	MAX(ProductCount) MaxProductCount,
	MIN(PairCount) MinPairCount,
	AVG(PairCount) AvgPairCount,
	MAX(PairCount) MaxPairCount
FROM (SELECT
	r.*,
	DATEDIFF(MINUTE, RunDate, EndDate) TotalDuration,
	CASE
		WHEN CapacityTransferRun = 1 THEN 'CapacityTransfer'
		WHEN StockClearanceRun = 1 THEN 'StockClearance'
		WHEN StockConsolidationRun = 1 THEN 'StockConsolidation'
		ELSE 'Performance'
	END RunType
FROM transfer.RunStatistics r
INNER JOIN transfer.transferruns t ON r.RunId = t.RunID
INNER JOIN engine.AlgoRuns a ON r.RunId = a.RunID
WHERE t.TransferTargetDate > '2021-01-01' AND EndDate IS NOT NULL) r
GROUP BY RunType
```
